addressType.description:

  • PRIMARY
  • RESIDENTIAL

  • If only primary address is provided, the value cannot be a post office box.
  • Alternate and Seasonal are not yet functional and may be added in the future.

Customer role short name.

If true, a house fiduciary custodian identified by the fund sponsor will be used for the customer role.
If false, a provided customer will be used for the customer role.

isCustomerIdentificationProcessExcluded.description: If true, the customer associated with this role will be excluded from Customer Identification Process (CIP).

isMailingWindowDisplayExcluded.description: If true, the customer name associated with this role will be excluded from the list of customer names in the mailing window.

isNonresidentAlienWithholdingEvaluationE.description: If true, the customer associated with this role will be excluded from the Nonresident Alien (NRA) withholding evaluation process.

isTaxResponsibleRole.description: If true, the customer role will be tax responsible.

isTuitionSavingsPlanBeneficiary.description:
If true, the customer associated with this role is the beneficial owner of a College Tuition Savings Plan.

Notes:
If true, the value of minimumCustomerCount and maximumCustomerCount must be 1.

maximumCustomerCount.description:
The maximum number of times the customer role is required for the account type.

Max Length: 3

minimumCustomerCount.description:
The minimum number of times the customer role is required for the account type.

Max Length: 3

contactMediumType.description:

  • TDD
  • PHONE
